creator: Icsus Apps
descriptionHtml:
Truth be told, this app was created because I wanted an app like this, but I couldn’t find it anywhere. Either the content was so shallow that a street cleaner could have given better advice, or there was no content at all- just a template with a heap of features.
I wanted an app that would turn habits into tasks and would organize them into the perfect routine, where all you would have to do is act. The tasks would be offered by the app. So I started creating this app. These were the main thought behind it:
As we know from a myriad of self-help books, it takes time for a habit to form. It’s only after 28 days, as the rule says, that it becomes a habit. Before that time, it’s a challenging task that we keep doing every day. That’s why I came up with the coin system. It keeps you from putting too much pressure on yourself. Besides, our brains are wired to greet any gift (be it a virtual coin) with a generous dose of dopamine.
The tasks are organized in a way that at first they are incredibly easy, becoming more and more complex in the process. This will make changing your behavior easier. The more complex tasks that appear later are a kind of a challenge, to keep you toned on the way to personal growth.
As time goes by, it will be up to you which tasks you want to add to your morning routine and which ones you can do with. In the “Coach” section, you will find carefully selected groups of tasks that solve particular problems.
The “Results” section is for motivating you. You can keep track of your success there and, having received a confidence boost, keep working to improve yourself.
descriptionShort: Train powerful morning habits to make a better version of yourself.
title: Powerful morning habits

creator: Icsus Apps
descriptionHtml:
This one-of-kind app is all you need to set healthy, good & simple habits, turn them into productive tasks & to do lists and get rewards as you go! Organize your routine to get most out of the day. Train your mind to follow the pre-scheduled tasks created by the app and track your progress.

This habit planner & tracker is built with simplicity, functionality & productivity at the core. Just input the habits you aim to build and the app will automatically turn them into powerfully effective tasks and organize them into the perfect routine for you to follow.
After setting concrete goals and tasks, Powerful Morning Habits will help you track your habits and activities, and let you know whether or not you have met your target.

The tasks offered by the app are incredibly easy at first, but they become progressively complex later in the process. This is done on purpose to keep you toned on the progress you make. The app will give you the chance to choose the tasks you want to add to your morning routine and will help you to build up your personal habits.

After the completion of your tasks, you will get virtual coins as a reward. The virtual coin rewards keep you motivated and prevent you from adding non-optimal amounts of tasks.
In our “Coach” section you will find customized packages of tasks that will solve particular problems. Finally, the “Results” section is there to help you track your habit-building progress and motivate you!


MAIN FEATURES:

📕 Simplicity - Simple interface that is super-easy to use and follow.
💡 Habit Management & Customization - Create the habits of your choice and plan your routine.
📊 Analytics - Track and analyze your progress for each of the habits set.
🏅 Rewards - Complete your tasks and get rewards to keep yourself on track!

Download the app today to improve your life. Slowly & easily build small habits by adding new, easy-to-achieve accomplishments. Change your habits to change your life!
